{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01SDc98mDcuhUGQ4rBa33FDb","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The migration is complete. Here's the final report:\n\n---\n\n### Migration Summary\n\n- **Frameworks:** `Quarkus 3.30.5` -> `Jakarta EE 10` (WildFly 31.0.1.Final)\n- **Overall outcome:** **Success** - All 7 smoke tests passed, application builds, deploys, and runs correctly.\n\n**High-level actions performed:**\n1. Replaced all Quarkus dependencies with `jakarta.jakartaee-api:10.0.0`\n2. Renamed packages from `quarkus.tutorial.order` to `jakarta.tutorial.order`\n3. Replaced Quarkus Qute templates with inline HTML generation in JAX-RS endpoints\n4. Replaced Quarkus `StartupEvent` with Jakarta EE `@Singleton @Startup @PostConstruct`\n5. Created standard JPA `persistence.xml` to replace Quarkus `application.properties`\n6. Changed packaging from Quarkus uber-jar to standard WAR deployed on WildFly\n7. Created JAX-RS `Application` class for endpoint registration\n\n### File Tree\n\n```\nModified:\n- pom.xml: Replaced Quarkus BOM/deps with Jakarta EE 10 API, war packaging\n- Dockerfile: Multi-stage build with Maven builder + WildFly runtime\n- smoke.py: New smoke test with 7 test cases\n\nAdded:\n- src/main/java/jakarta/tutorial/order/web/OrderApplication.java: JAX-RS Application class\n- src/main/resources/META-INF/persistence.xml: JPA configuration\n- src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/beans.xml: CDI 4.0 configuration\n- src/main/webapp/css/default.css: Static CSS (moved from resources/)\n- CHANGELOG.md: Full migration log\n\nRemoved:\n- src/main/java/quarkus/ (entire old package tree)\n- src/main/resources/application.properties (Quarkus config)\n- src/main/resources/templates/ (Qute templates: orders.html, lineItems.html, orderTemplate.html, lineItemTemplate.html)\n- src/main/resources/css/default.css (moved to webapp/)\n- src/main/docker/ (Quarkus Docker variants)\n\nMigrated (package rename + code changes):\n-